    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped tomato </strong>and <strong>charred pineapple</strong> with most of the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> (save some for garnish!), your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your<strong> pineapple salsa</strong></p>",
