    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a slit into the top of each<strong> hot dog bun</strong></p><p>Remove the sausage tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>cut</strong> <strong>hot dog bun[s]</strong> to the other side of the sausage tray[s] and return the tray[s] to the oven for 2-3 min or until the hot dog buns are warmed through</p>",
