      "instruction": "<p>Fill each<strong> hot dog bun </strong>with a <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>hot dog</strong>, then top with some of the <strong>pineapple salsa</strong>, <strong>teriyaki sauce</strong>, the<strong> reserved sliced spring onion </strong>and some of the <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>remaining sriracha mayo</strong> and the <strong>remaining pineapple salsa</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
